Schedule A – Service-specific details
BATTLESHIP
Battleship is an interactive Game available for download on iOS and Android mobile and tablet devices, Nintendo Switch devices and PC from the App Store, Google Play, Nintendo Switch and Steam.
Battleship is categorised as a Family Friendly Game for players of all ages. For more information see Section 4 (Parents and Children).
When you play Battleship we may share certain information we collect about you with third parties including: Gamesparks; Unity 3D; Apps Flyer; Facebook and PlayFab
CLUE: CLASSIC EDITION
Clue: Classic Edition (also known as Cluedo: Classic Edition or Clue/Cluedo The Classic Mystery Game) is an interactive Game available for download on iOS and Android mobile and tablet devices, Nintendo Switch devices and PC from the App Store, Google Play, Nintendo Switch and Steam.
Clue: Classic Edition is not intended for or directed at, children and we do not knowingly or intentionally collect or process data relating to any such children who may be playing it.
When you play Clue: Classic Edition we may share certain information we collect about you with third parties including: Playfab; Photon; Firebase Crashlytics; Apps Flyer; Unity 3D and Facebook.
Apple Arcade
Clue: Classic Edition is also available on Apple Arcade as Clue: Classic Edition+ (or Cluedo: Classic Edition+).  In that version of the game, we only share certain information with the following third party services:
Photon
: this service collects your IP address for the purpose of multiplayer matchmaking and functionality.
Apple iCloud
:  this service collects game play data which is stored in your iCloud account storage.  This allows you to save your game progress and sync your game across devices.  You may decline to store data in iCloud at any time.  To turn off iCloud data storage, you must turn off iCloud in Apple Settings for our game.
Apple Game Center
:  this service links the game with your Apple Game Center account.  If you are signed into Game Center on your Apple device, Apple will receive your gameplay activity.  To stop sending data to Game Center, you must sign out of Game Center in Apple Settings.
CLUE 2024 / CLUEDO 2024
Clue 2024 (also known as “Cluedo 2024” on mobile platforms or “Clue” or “Cluedo” or console platforms) is a new version of the interactive Game based on the Clue/Cluedo board game available for download on iOS and Android mobile and tablet devices and PC from Steam.
Clue 2024 is not intended for or directed at, children and we do not knowingly or intentionally collect or process data relating to any such children who may be playing it.
Clue 2024 integrates a limited version of our optional Bubble feature which enables players to save their progress in the cloud. We disable this feature for any Children we identify playing the game.
When you play Clue 2024 we may share certain information we collect about you with third parties including: Playfab; Photon; Firebase Crashlytics; Apps Flyer; Unity 3D, Google, Apple and Facebook.
