MONOPOLY
Monopoly, the popular Hasbro board game, is an interactive mobile Game available for download on iOS and Android mobile and tablet devices and Sky TV from the App Store, Google Play and Sky.
Monopoly is categorised as a Family Friendly Game for players of all ages. For more information see Section 4 (Parents and Children).
Monopoly integrates our optional Bubble feature which enables you to seamlessly text and video chat with friend in-game while you play. We disable this feature for any Children we identify as playing the Game.
When you play Monopoly we may share certain information we collect about you with third parties including: Playfab; Photon; Firebase Crashlytics; Facebook; Apps Flyer; Unity 3D; Google; Apple; AGORA; Facebook and Mailchimp.
